parameters:
Underling: Ugh... It's embarrassing, but the betrayal among
our organization's members is relentless... Nearly half of
the underlings have already gone over to the mayor's side...

Memimi: ...It can't be helped... Our organization is
essentially in ruins... Even though the big boss managed to
escape, the chances of revival are... extremely low...

Orca Asparagus-Mayor: Shashasha... You underlings over there
can betray us anytime you want, you know? I'll treat you
better than being locked up here!

Memimi: (Even if we join him, we'll just be worked to the
bone and discarded... But staying with our organization
might mean no future at all... If someone betrays us here,
who could blame them...)

Underling: Who would follow someone like you... We won't
join the ranks of someone who would do such terrible things
to Lord Shark Duke...

Underling: Those who betray us were never worth anything to
begin with!! We're different... We're the true members who
swore loyalty to the big boss!!

Orca Asparagus-Mayor: I'm looking forward to seeing how long
that resolve lasts... I've got a special event planned for
today. When it's over, I wonder how many of you will still
be standing?

Underling: When I joined the organization, I thought
unifying the city was impossible, but thanks to Lord Shark's
achievements, it's starting to feel real. If you don't
forget hope, anything can happen.

Memimi: Never give up on your dreams... I will continue to
fight as many times as necessary to achieve my goal. You all
should just believe in me and Lord Shark Broccoli, and
follow us relentlessly...

Underling: (Above all, seeing Lord Shark's numerous lewd
forms was like a dream come true... The cameras in the
shower room have been removed, but I've saved recordings for
days and watched them over and over... Even though I know
it's wrong, there's no way I can delete the data...)

Memimi: It seems you're trembling with emotion... you've
gone silent...

Underling: I never imagined the mayor would show up... That
bastard, so brazen...! And if we lose, Lord Shark Broccoli
making an AV debut?! I really want to see it, but he's
taking us lightly...!
Memimi: Did I let a bit of my true feelings slip...? Hey...

Underling: This... is a gift from me! I bought it with my
own money... "Delicious Powder," please eat it!! As someone
involved in the powder refining business, I can't let the
recipe fall into anyone else's hands no matter what...

Memimi: Thank you... I also want to protect the Delicious
Powder. This powder, Lord Shark Broccoli's masterpiece, I
won't hand it over to anyone...

You ate the nutrient-rich powder and felt energized! Max HP
increased by 50!

Underling: Was it three years ago that Shark Broccoli-sama
was picked up by the big boss? This organization was founded
five years ago, and back then, Monster Fight didn't even
exist yet...

Memimi: I've heard that Monster Fight started about two
years ago. The big boss initially didn't intend to bring me
into the dark organization, so I'm not very familiar with
the details from that time... I joined the organization a
year ago, and my debut in Monster Fight was half a year ago.

Underling: That's some rapid promotion... Now Shark
Broccoli-sama has become one of the most important figures
in the dark organization, on the verge of unifying the
city... Seriously amazing...

Memimi: The one I need to repay isn't just Shark Broccoli-
sama... It's also everyone in the organization who has
walked with me and sometimes guided me. I truly am grateful
to all the people around me...

Underling: You don't have to worry about that...! Just being
able to see you in sexy outfits and being allowed to fondle
your breasts is more than I could ever ask for...!

Memimi: That wasn't meant as a show of gratitude...! Damn
it... I've ended up exposing my shame to close
acquaintances... My personal relationships are... ugh...

Underling: Lord Shark... if Shark Mountain-san loses and has
to make an AV debut...! I absolutely hate that idea... I
want her to be only mine... I do want to see Shark Mountain-
san having sex, but I don't want her to do it with anyone
but me...!!

Memimi: Calm down... that's disgusting!! Stop repeating
'sex' over and over!!

Underling: But even if you say that... just watching her on
TV forcefully having her way with celebrities, I felt like I
was going to lose it, and now to think she has to sleep
around with other men as a routine... it does give me a bit
of a hard-on, but...

Memimi: ...Seriously, just shut up... I get how you feel,
but...

Underling: At least, take this...! It's a heart necklace
that I chose!! Please wear it and defeat Mayor Orca...!!

Memimi: That's creepy... no, I mean... uh, I'll just accept
the sentiment... thank you...

With the underling's feelings received, Memimi's attack
power increased slightly...
